{"title":"TRed SpeedWay Kartodrome fixie is a track bike built for urban Go Kart racing!","link":"https://bikerumor.com/2021/06/23/tred-speedway-kartodrome-fixie-is-a-track-bike-built-for-urban-go-kart-racing/","date":1624466558000,"content":"<div id=\"readability-page-1\" class=\"page\"><div><p>TRed’s all-new SpeedWay Kartodrome completely reimagines their classic Manaia track bike for the unique flat go kart track racing that’s growing in the urban fixie racing scene. With huge volume tires and totally reshaped geometry built for flat, high-speed cornering, the SpeedWay Kartodrome debuted with a win and a podium at the Italian Fixed Gear National Championships last weekend, and could be coming to your indoor asphalt racing scene or even city streets soon…</p><h2>TRed SpeedWay Kartodrome flat track cart racing fixed gear</h2><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/22132836/TRed-SpeedWay-Kartodrome-flat-track-cart-racing-fixed-gear-bike_lets-go-carting.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/22132836/TRed-SpeedWay-Kartodrome-flat-track-cart-racing-fixed-gear-bike_lets-go-carting.jpg?ezimgfmt=rs:484x372/rscb19/ng:webp/ngcb19\" alt=\"TRed SpeedWay Kartodrome flat track cart racing fixed gear bike, urban fixie racing,&nbsp;Francesca Selva, 2021 Italian Fixed Gear Champion\" width=\"1300\" height=\"1000\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/22132836/TRed-SpeedWay-Kartodrome-flat-track-cart-racing-fixed-gear-bike_lets-go-carting.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb19 1300w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/22132836/TRed-SpeedWay-Kartodrome-flat-track-cart-racing-fixed-gear-bike_lets-go-carting-297x228.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb19 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/202