www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/22132801/TRed-SpeedWay-Kartodrome-flat-track-cart-racing-fixed-gear-bike_complete-297x178.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/22132801/TRed-SpeedWay-Kartodrome-flat-track-cart-racing-fixed-gear-bike_complete-800x480.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/22132801/TRed-SpeedWay-Kartodrome-flat-track-cart-racing-fixed-gear-bike_complete-120x72.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/22132801/TRed-SpeedWay-Kartodrome-flat-track-cart-racing-fixed-gear-bike_complete-768x461.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/22132801/TRed-SpeedWay-Kartodrome-flat-track-cart-racing-fixed-gear-bike_complete-1536x922.jpg 1536w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/22132801/TRed-SpeedWay-Kartodrome-flat-track-cart-racing-fixed-gear-bike_complete-696x418.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/22132801/TRed-SpeedWay-Kartodrome-flat-track-cart-racing-fixed-gear-bike_complete-1068x641.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/22132801/TRed-SpeedWay-Kartodrome-flat-track-cart-racing-fixed-gear-bike_complete-1920x1152.jpg 1920w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/22132801/TRed-SpeedWay-Kartodrome-flat-track-cart-racing-fixed-gear-bike_complete-700x420.jpg 700w\"></a>Set against a black background, the end result almost looks like a regular track bike from the side – albeit with unconventionally small steel tubing and significantly dropped seatstays.</p><p>But there’s no denying that this is a very unique bike, adapted specifically for a very niche style of racing. The question is what it might be like to ride outside of a go kart track?</p><h3>TRed SpeedWay Kartodrome kart racing fixie – Real availability &amp; options?</h3><figure id=\"attachment_262617\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-262617\"><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/23101927/TRed-SpeedWay-Kartodrome-flat-track-cart-racing-fixed-gear_fixie-race-photo-by-Geme-Omar-DeLazzari_Italian-fixed-gear-champion-Francesca-Selva-corner.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/23101927/TRed-SpeedWay-Kartodrome-flat-track-cart-racing-fixed-gear_fixie-race-photo-by-Geme-Omar-DeLazzari_Italian-fixed-gear-champion-Francesca-Selva-corner.jpg\" alt=\"TRed SpeedWay Kartodrome flat track cart racing fixed gear bike, urban fixie racing,&nbsp;Francesca Selva, 2021 Italian Fixed Gear Champion, racing photo by Geme Omar DeLazzari\" width=\"1600\" height=\"900\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/23101927/TRed-SpeedWay-Kartodrome-flat-track-cart-racing-fixed-gear_fixie-race-photo-by-Geme-Omar-DeLazzari_Italian-fixed-gear-champion-Francesca-Selva-corner.jpg 1600w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/23101927/TRed-SpeedWay-Kartodrome-flat-track-cart-racing-fixed-gear_fixie-race-photo-by-Geme-Omar-DeLazzari_Italian-fixed-gear-champion-Francesca-Selva-corner-297x167.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/23101927/TRed-SpeedWay-Kartodrome-flat-track-cart-racing-fixed-gear_fixie-race-photo-by-Geme-Omar-DeLazzari_Italian-fixed-gear-champion-Francesca-Selva-corner-800x450.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/23101927/TRed-SpeedWay-Kartodrome-flat-track-cart-racing-fixed-gear_fixie-race-photo-by-Geme-