azonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/23101927/TRed-SpeedWay-Kartodrome-flat-track-cart-racing-fixed-gear_fixie-race-photo-by-Geme-Omar-DeLazzari_Italian-fixed-gear-champion-Francesca-Selva-corner-747x420.jpg 747w\"></a><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-262617\">photo by <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/geme_omar/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Geme Omar De Lazzari</a></figcaption></figure><p>The new bike was ultimately ridden to a decisive Italian Fixed Gear Championship win by&nbsp;Selva in its debut race (and a second place in the men’s race by Alessandro Mariani in his first day riding the new bike!)</p><p>Now, does any consumer really need a flat track kart racing fixed gear race bike? TRed thinks there could be a real (<em>but admittedly small</em>) market for the SpeedWay Kartodrome, so they do plan to make it available to consumers later this summer.</p><p>They have three variations in the works to make the unique bike more real-world-usable to a wider range of urban cyclists…</p><figure id=\"attachment_262505\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-262505\"><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/22132754/TRed-SpeedWay-Kartodrome-flat-track-cart-racing-fixed-gear_photo-by-Geme-Omar-DeLazzari_Campionato-Italiano-Scatto-Fisso_Italian-fixed-gear-champion-Francesca-Selva.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/22132754/TRed-SpeedWay-Kartodrome-flat-track-cart-racing-fixed-gear_photo-by-Geme-Omar-DeLazzari_Campionato-Italiano-Scatto-Fisso_Italian-fixed-gear-champion-Francesca-Selva.jpg\" alt=\"TRed SpeedWay Kartodrome flat track cart racing fixed gear bike, urban fixie racing,&nbsp;Francesca Selva, 2021 Italian Fixed Gear Champion win\" width=\"1500\" height=\"844\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/22132754/TRed-SpeedWay-Kartodrome-flat-track-cart-racing-fixed-gear_photo-by-Geme-Omar-DeLazzari_Campionato-Italiano-Scatto-Fisso_Italian-fixed-gear-champion-Francesca-Selva.jpg 1500w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/22132754/TRed-SpeedWay-Kartodrome-flat-track-cart-racing-fixed-gear_photo-by-Geme-Omar-DeLazzari_Campionato-Italiano-Scatto-Fisso_Italian-fixed-gear-champion-Francesca-Selva-297x167.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/22132754/TRed-SpeedWay-Kartodrome-flat-track-cart-racing-fixed-gear_photo-by-Geme-Omar-DeLazzari_Campionato-Italiano-Scatto-Fisso_Italian-fixed-gear-champion-Francesca-Selva-800x450.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/22132754/TRed-SpeedWay-Kartodrome-flat-track-cart-racing-fixed-gear_photo-by-Geme-Omar-DeLazzari_Campionato-Italiano-Scatto-Fisso_Italian-fixed-gear-champion-Francesca-Selva-120x68.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/22132754/TRed-SpeedWay-Kartodrome-flat-track-cart-racing-fixed-gear_photo-by-Geme-Omar-DeLazzari_Campionato-Italiano-Scatto-Fisso_Italian-fixed-gear-champion-Francesca-Selva-768x432.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/22132754/TRed-SpeedWay-Kartodrome-flat-track-cart-racing-fixed-gear_photo-by-Geme-Omar-DeLazzari_Campionato-Italiano-Scatto-Fisso_Italian-fixed-gear-champion-Francesca-Selva-696x392.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/22132754/TRed-SpeedWay-Kartodrome-flat-track-cart-racing-fixed-gear_photo-by-Geme-Omar-DeLazzari_Campionato-Italiano-Scatto-Fisso_Italian-fixed-gear-champion-Francesca-Selva-1068x601.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/22132754/TRed-SpeedWay-Kartodrome-flat-track-cart-racing-fixed-gear_photo-by-Geme-Omar-DeLazzari_Campionato-Italiano-Scatto-Fisso_Italian-fixed-gear-champion-Francesca-Selva-746x420.jpg 746w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1500px) 100vw, 1500px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb19 src ng ngcb19 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/22132754/TRed-SpeedWay-Kartodrome-flat-track-cart-racing-fixed-gear_photo-by-Geme-Omar-DeLazzari_Campionato-Italiano-Scatto-Fisso_Italian-fixed-gear-champion-Francesca-Selva.jpg\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/22132754/TRed-SpeedWay-Kartodrome-flat-track-cart-racing-fixed-gear_photo-by-Geme-Omar-DeLazzari_Campionato-Italiano-Scatto-Fisso_Italian-fixed-gear-champion-Francesca-Selva.jpg 1500w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/22132754/TRed-SpeedWay-Kartodrome-flat-track-cart-racing-fixed-gear_photo-by-Geme-Omar-DeLazzari_Campionato-Italiano-Scatto-Fisso_Italian-fixed-gear-champion-Francesca-Selva-297x167.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/22132754/TRed-SpeedWay-Kartodrome-flat-track-cart-racing-fixed-gear_photo-by-Geme-Omar-DeLazzari_Campionato-Italiano-Scatto-Fisso_Italian-fixed-gear-champion-Francesca-Selva-800x450.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/22132754/TRed-SpeedWay-Kartodrome-flat-track-cart-racing-fixed-gear_photo-by-Geme-Omar-DeLazzari_Campionato-Italiano-Scatto-Fisso_Italian-fixed-gear-champion-Francesca-Selva-120x68.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/22132754/TRed-SpeedWay-Kartodrome-flat-track-cart-racing-fixed-gear_photo-by-Geme-Omar-DeLazzari_Campionato-Italiano-Scatto-Fisso_Italian-fixed-gear-champion-Francesca-Selva-768x432.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/22132754/TRed-SpeedWay-Kartodrome-flat-track-cart-racing-fixed-gear_photo-by-Geme-Omar-DeLazzari_Campionato-Italiano-Scatto-Fisso_Italian-fixed-gear-champion-Francesca-Selva-696x392.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/22132754/TRed-SpeedWay-Kartodrome-flat-track-cart-racing-fixed-gear_photo-by-Geme-Omar-DeLazzari_Campionato-Italiano-Scatto-Fisso_Italian-fixed-gear-champion-Francesca-Selva-1068x601.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/22132754/TRed-SpeedWay-Kartodrome-flat-track-cart-racing-fixed-gear_photo-by-Geme-Omar-DeLazzari_Campionato-Italiano-Scatto-Fisso_Italian-fixed-gear-champion-Francesca-Selva-746x420.jpg 746w\"></a><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-262505\">c. TRed, racing photos by <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/geme_omar/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Geme Omar De Lazzari</a></figcaption></figure><p>The core TRed SpeedWay Kartodrome will be a brakeless fixed gear race bike just like Selva raced to the championship win above. Then, a TRed SpeedWay UrbanFighter version will add in a front disc brake for more street riding versatility, plus the option to have a fixed or singlespeed freewheel rear wheel, or even the power-regenerating e-bike rear wheel tech we saw in their <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/2017/03/23/treds-wild-fixed-gear-regenerative-bestianera-hybrid-streetfighter-urban-e-bike/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">BestiaNera Hybrid</a> a few years back! Lastly, this autumn a SpeedWay DirtyFighter will be added too, likely with off-road tires suitable for gravel flat track racing or a bit of junkyard cross? Only time will tell on that one.</p><p>How much it will actually cost is still up in the air, but TRed says the price will be “nothing crazy” so we expect it somewhere closer to the ~2000€ alloy <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/2017/04/14/tred-aracnide-a02a-ool-ultra-premium-5-9kg-steel-road-bike-plus-scandium-manaia-track/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Manaia track</a> frameset, rather than the more complete ~4000€ alloy <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/2019/08/20/tred-horkokhan-slips-in-modern-aero-alloy-stayer-bike-for-motor-paced-track-racing/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Horkokhan stayer</a> frameset &amp; cockpit kit.</p><p><a href=\"http://tredbikes.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><em>TRedbikes.com</em></a></p></div></div>","author":"Cory Benson","siteTitle":"Bikerumor","siteHash":"49f427af0a926f4232eb837006841d7242e153e3afbb590f32e4b104ea3e2718","entryHash":"276a4c50062805838bfdbd36a011de92f67ffacc5185c73a3973327dcac5ad6a","category":"Cycling"}